This paper proposes a new scene text detection method based on neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The method also involves character-level annotations and affinity between characters, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions experiments and benchmarks, which are often associated with information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
